author: Alysha Tsuji
title: UCLA cheerleader takes scary hard fall, then is dropped while being carried off court
text:
UCLA cheerleader takes scary hard fall, then is dropped while being carried off court For The Win 17 hrs ago Alysha Tsuji Replay Video SETTINGS OFF HD HQ SD LO A UCLA cheerleader took a hard fall during a performance in a break in the game vs. Oregon on Thursday night. Then, to make things worse, as she was being carried off the floor, the man carrying her slipped and fell.
This poor UCLA cheerleader fell from the pyramid, then the guy carrying her off slips & falls on top of her (h/t @AJPONE ) pic.twitter.com/cYeaiJowxL
- CJ Fogler (@cjzero) February 10, 2017
Per Bruin Report Online , she was able to walk off the court.
Cheerleader walks off to applause, but she is shaken up.
- Bruin Report Online (@BruinReport) February 10, 2017
Hopefully she's OK.
